11 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
12 Sec. 1. MOTOR VEHICLE PURCHASE CANCELLATION; STUDY
13 COMMITTEE; REPORT
14 (a) Creation. There is created the Motor Vehicle Purchase Cancellation
15 Study Committee to examine the possibility of amending Vermont’s laws to
16 permit persons to cancel or rescind the purchase of a motor vehicle under
17 certain circumstances.
18 (b) Membership. The Committee shall be composed of the following
19 members:
20 (1) the Commissioner of Motor Vehicles or designee;
